---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="İhracat"
  description="Yiğiter Orman Ürünleri — Door frame and architrave manufacturer, exporting to Europe, Middle East, Central Asia and Africa. Regular shipments, international quality standards."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-primary text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Export / İhracat</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          4 Kıtaya Düzenli İhracat
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Avrupa, Orta Doğu, Türki Cumhuriyetler ve Afrika pazarlarına
          kapı kasası ve pervaz ihracatı yapıyoruz. Kendi üretimimiz,
          uluslararası kalite standartlarında.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="/iletisim/teklif-al?urun=%C4%B0hracat+Talebi"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            İhracat Talebi Gönder
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#ihracat-pazarlari"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white/25 transition-colors"
          >
            Pazarlar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- İhracat Pazarları -->
  <section id="ihracat-pazarlari" class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">İhracat Pazarlarımız</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Dört farklı coğrafyaya düzenli ve sürekli sevkiyat yapıyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
        {[
          {
            bolge: 'Avrupa',
            renk: 'bg-blue-50 border-blue-200',
            textColor: 'text-blue-900',
            subColor: 'text-blue-700',
            icon: '🇪🇺',
            aciklama: 'Batı ve Doğu Avrupa ülkeleri',
          },
          {
            bolge: 'Orta Doğu',
            renk: 'bg-amber-50 border-amber-200',
            textColor: 'text-amber-900',
            subColor: 'text-amber-700',
            icon: '🌍',
            aciklama: 'Irak, Suriye, Körfez ülkeleri ve komşu bölgeler',
          },
          {
            bolge: 'Türki Cumhuriyetler',
            renk: 'bg-red-50 border-red-200',
            textColor: 'text-red-900',
            subColor: 'text-red-700',
            icon: '🌏',
            aciklama: 'Orta Asya ve Türki Cumhuriyetler',
          },
          {
            bolge: 'Afrika',
            renk: 'bg-green-50 border-green-200',
            textColor: 'text-green-900',
            subColor: 'text-green-700',
            icon: '🌍',
            aciklama: 'Kuzey ve Sahra altı Afrika pazarları',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class={`border rounded-2xl p-6 ${item.renk}`}>
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">{item.icon}</div>
            <h3 class={`text-lg font-bold mb-2 ${item.textColor}`}>{item.bolge}</h3>
            <p class={`text-sm leading-relaxed ${item.subColor}`}>{item.aciklama}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- İhracat Ürünleri -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-5">İhracat Ürünleri</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            İhracat portföyümüz ağırlıklı olarak <strong class="text-gray-900">kendi tesisimizde
            ürettiğimiz kapı komponentlerinden</strong> oluşmaktadır.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="/urunler/kapi-komponentleri/kasa" class="group flex items-start gap-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Kapı Kasası</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Standart ve özel ölçü. Kendi üretimimiz.</p>
              </div>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors ml-auto shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </a>

            <a href="/urunler/kapi-komponentleri/pervaz" class="group flex items-start gap-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 10h16M4 14h16M4 18h16" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Kapı Pervazı</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Klasik, modern ve özel profil. Kendi üretimimiz.</p>
              </div>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors ml-auto shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Neden Yiğiter -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-5">Neden Yiğiter?</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Üreticiden direkt — aracısız fiyat ve doğrudan iletişim',
              'Uluslararası kalite standartlarında üretim',
              'Düzenli ve sürekli sevkiyat kapasitesi',
              'Standart ve özel ölçü üretim esnekliği',
              '20+ yıllık ihracat deneyimi',
              'Türkiye\'nin köklü kapı komponenti üreticilerinden',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>

          <a
            href="/hakkimizda/ihracat"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-accent font-semibold text-sm mt-6 transition-colors"
          >
            Detaylı İhracat Bilgisi
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- İhracat CTA -->
  <section class="bg-primary text-white py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">İhracat Ortağı Arıyorsanız</h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            Türkiye'den düzenli kapı komponenti tedariki için bizimle iletişime geçin.
            Teklif ve ürün bilgisi için formumuzu doldurun.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 lg:justify-end">
          <a
            href="/iletisim/teklif-al?urun=%C4%B0hracat+Talebi"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            İhracat Talebi
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/905418187667" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
